'''Bangumi 番组计划'''是一个中文[[ACG|ACG]]互联网分享与交流项目，由网友“Sai”于2008年在[[中國|中國]][[廣西壯族自治區|廣西]][[桂林市|桂林]]建立<ref name="qq">{{cite web|title=超萌Bangumi娘发售 制作过程全解|url=http://comic.qq.com/a/20110829/000044.htm#p=1|author=腾讯动漫|date=2011-08-29|accessdate=2015-05-18|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2019-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924162932/https://ac.qq.com/#p=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url = http://www.jpbeta.net/2011/08/bangumi-niang/|title = 国内原创手办Bangumi娘简介|accessdate = 2015-05-18|author = jpbeta|date = 2011-08-23|publisher = |language = zh-cn|archive-date = 2015-05-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518203401/http://www.jpbeta.net/2011/08/bangumi-niang/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="c">{{cite web|title = Bangumi:番组计划动漫游戏分享社区|url = http://www.egouz.com/topics/8784.html|author = egouz|date = 2014-04-03|accessdate = 2015-05-26|language = zh-cn|archive-date = 2015-05-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150529052627/http://www.egouz.com/topics/8784.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==简介==
该项目最初以“'''[[Chobits|Chobits]]”'''（[[CLAMP|CLAMP]]所著之日本漫画名）作为开发代号，喻指“人性的电脑”和“完整的ACG资料库”。2009年在项目参与者Senken的协助下，“Chobits”被正式命名为'''Bangumi 番组计划'''（“Bangumi”一词为日文“{{lang|ja|番組}}”的罗马音拼写），并于2009年1月25日上线。项目上线第二日会员数量达到2000，并在随后达到20000名以上；其建立初衷是致力于让ACG爱好者在欣赏ACG作品时拥有一个轻松便捷独特的交流与沟通环境<ref name="qq" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = http://bangumi.tv/about|title = 关于 Bangumi 番组计划|accessdate = 2015-05-18|author = Bangumi.tv|date = 2011-04-23|publisher = |archive-date = 2015-05-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150520042831/http://bangumi.tv/about|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

目前该项目已推出网页和[[个人电脑|PC]]桌面客户端<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://bangumi.tv/onair|title = Bangumi番组计划onAir桌面客户端|accessdate = 2017-06-28|author = bangumi.tv|date = 2012-09-12|publisher = |language = zh-cn|archive-date = 2017-07-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170707204836/http://bangumi.tv/onair|dead-url = no}}</ref>；第三方开发者亦根据网页制作了适用于[[iOS|iOS]]、[[Android|Android]]和[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]的移动客户端<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://cn.appszoom.com/android_applications/tools/bangumi_ctcpf.html|title = Bangumi番组计划|accessdate = 2015-05-18|author = Appszoom|date = |publisher = |archive-date = 2015-05-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150526192130/http://cn.appszoom.com/android_applications/tools/bangumi_ctcpf.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://dl.pconline.com.cn/download/348035.html|title = Bangumi番组计划 For WP7 WP8 1.0.0.0|accessdate = 2015-05-18|author = 太平洋电脑网|date = 2013-02-26|publisher = |archive-date = 2015-05-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150526191829/http://dl.pconline.com.cn/download/348035.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://bangumi.tv/group/topic/32239|title = Bangumi iOS客户端|author = bangumi.tv|accessdate = 2015-05-26|date = 2014-04-30|archive-date = 2015-05-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150526172550/http://bangumi.tv/group/topic/32239|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

该项目的网站吉祥物为“Bangumi娘”，形象为粉髮的[[美少女|美少女]]<ref name=":1" />。

== 功能 ==
Bangumi 番组计划基于[[CC_BY-SA协议|CC BY-SA协议]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://bangumi.tv/about/copyright|title = Bangumi 番组计划版权声明|accessdate = 2015-05-18|author = bangumi.tv|date = |publisher = |archive-date = 2015-05-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518185429/http://bangumi.tv/about/copyright|dead-url = no}}</ref>，保存由用户提供的各类ACG相关事物和人物、[[电影|电影]]、[[电视剧|电视剧]]等的相关资料，可以让使用者查阅，并提供BBS论坛和留言版供交流探讨。

该项目还会公布其用户对收录事物的评价，并发布排行榜<ref name=":0" />。

